metadata.name: Skywalkers Film Token
metadata.description:
This genesis edition serves to fund the production of itsdavey's upcoming short film scheduled to premier Q2 2023. This film will provide context to and further develop the Skywalkers story. 

- All minters will get their name or ENS in the credits of the film. 
- Mint 5 or more tokens to receive an Associate Producer credit. 
- Mint 10 or more tokens to receive an Executive Producer credit.  

Future and expanded utility of these tokens is at the sole discretion of itsdavey ;)
